Package: voicer
Version: 1.0.0
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libx11-6, xdotool, pulseaudio
Installed-Size: SIZE_PLACEHOLDER
Maintainer: Voicer <voicer@voicer.app>
Description: Offline speech-to-text with push-to-talk hotkeys
 Cross-platform application for voice input. Runs in the system tray,
 recognizes Russian speech offline using the GigaAM v3 model,
 and delivers results via WebSocket or by inserting text at the cursor.
